731244f-b.text:
Celebrations, Parades and Municipal Events:
Two southward views down Fifth Avenue, from 36th
Street, showing rnilitary units paradirg up the
Avenue. The photographers vantage point is the
adjoining structure to the building at the N.W.
corner. On the left is the easterly side of this
thoroughfare. The white columned building is
B. Altman's Department Store.
